comments: Nurkic (POR) and Barnes (SAC) engage and disengage with one another in the lane.
Barnes (SAC) extends his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Covington's (POR) front during the driving shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) reflexively places his arms around Covington's (POR) upper half before quickly removing them.
Holmes (SAC) and Nurkic (POR) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Hield (SAC) makes clean contact with the ball during Covington's (POR) upward shooting motion, and Holmes (SAC) cleanly blocks Hield's shot attempt thereafter.
Nurkic (POR) and Holmes (SAC) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Nurkic (POR) and Holmes (SAC) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Holmes (SAC) makes incidental "high-five" contact with McCollum (POR) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Jones Jr. (POR) and Hield (SAC) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Hield (SAC) initiates contact across Jones Jr.'s (POR) arm after he gains control of the pass and affects the alley-oop attempt.
Hield (SAC) is already in Jones Jr.'s (POR) path and marginal body contact occurs as they move along the perimeter.
Holmes (SAC) extends his right arm forward onto Covington's (POR) midsection as he sets the screen, and marginal contact occurs as the pass to the corner is made.
Holmes (SAC) rests his hand on McCollum's (POR) right arm and then disengages as marginal contact occurs during rebounding.
Holmes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in McCollum's (POR) path following the hand-off and absorbs the side-to-side contact.
Nurkic (POR) is jumping to the side of Hield (SAC) and would have missed him if Hield didn't extend his left arm to initiate the marginal contact.
Covington (POR) has his left arm extended forward when marginal contact occurs with Barnes' (SAC) front during the follow-through of his put-back attempt.
Haliburton (SAC) commits the take foul on Lillard (POR).
Lillard (POR) legally contests Hield's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
Holmes (SAC) attempts to commit a take foul on Covington (POR) and the contact is marginal.
